headline: Nvidia, healthcare stocks, Axon: Market Minute
summary: Josh Lipton outlines some of the day's trending stories on this segment of Market Minute. Nvidia's (NVDA) shares rise ahead of its earnings report, with options markets anticipating an 8.5% move in either direction. Meanwhile, hospital health insurance stocks, such as Molina Health (MOH), Centene (CNC), and Community Health (CYH), are falling after budget cuts were passed by the House of Representatives that could impact health programs. Axon Enterprise (AXON) shares are soaring after the company exceeded earnings expectations for the fourth quarter and offered a positive outlook for the full year. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute. This post was written by Josh Lynch
